      <body>I've experienced the same bug when uncommenting the line about 'config.i18n.load_path' in rails3 config/application.rb

Rails 2.x defined the RAILS_ROOT in config/boot.rb before anything else and I think setting Rails.root at the same place might make sense.</body>
